    %h1 Painless and paperless.
    %p 
      Storm Savvy enables busy professionals to overcome 
      the burden of paperwork by streamlining web-enabled 
      technologies such as PDF rendering, email 
      notifications and streaming public API data.
    %p
      While we are living in the electronic age, most 
      aspects of professional life are dictated by the 
      ability to fill out and process lots of paperwork 
      quickly.
    %p
      Although the exchange of information is a vital 
      part of modern life, the time investment required 
      to manage paperwork frequently impedes progress on 
      projects and increases the company's carbon 
      foot print.
